Package plasystem_gui

package plasystem_gui
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AddProductGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for adding new product data to the application.
    AddUserAccountGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for adding new user accounts to the application.
    EditProductGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for editing existing product data in the application.
    EditUserAccountGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for editing existing user accounts in the application.
    LaunchPanelGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window serving as the login panel for the application.
    LowStockGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for displaying products with low stock levels.
    MainProgramGUI
    The main window of the application, displaying product data in a table and providing controls for managing products, transactions, restocking, and user accounts.
    ReceiptInvoiceGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for displaying a receipt invoice.
    RestockHistoryGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for displaying the history of restock operations.
    RestockProductGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for restocking products.
    RHDetailsGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for displaying the details of a restock operation.
    RHDetailsGUI.DecimalFormatRenderer
    Inner renderer to format double values to two decimal places.
    RHDetailsGUI.PriceTableRenderer
    Custom renderer to format and align price columns in the table.
    THDetailsGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for displaying the details of a transaction.
    THDetailsGUI.DecimalFormatRenderer
    Inner renderer to format double values to two decimal places.
    THDetailsGUI.PriceTableRenderer
    Custom renderer to format and align price columns in the table.
    TransactionGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for handling product transactions.
    TransactionHistoryGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for displaying the history of transactions.
    UserAccountsGUI
    A graphical user interface (GUI) window for managing user accounts.
